name: PSTricks Graph Editor
tagline: A Java SE desktop program for LaTeX, PSTricks users.
body:
### PSTricks Graph Editor.
A Java SE desktop program, providing a convenient, user friendly interface for drawing PSTricks graphs, and can automatically generate the PSTricks commands according to the graph objects on its interface. User can free from recalling the complicated PSTricks commands by just copying & pasting the generated commands into any LaTeX documents.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
